n mass and $p_T$, and within\nthe statistical accuracy no nuclear modification is seen.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Feb 2017 17:21:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Jul 2017 15:18:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-23"}
