hermal fluctuations for a Bjorken expansion\nand determine the coefficient of the first fractional power ($\\propto 1/(\\tau\nT)^{3/2}$) of the nonlinear noise corrections to energy momentum tensor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Feb 2017 23:27:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-07"}
