 a low dependence on microtubule and active force\ngenerator exact numbers or dynamics, provided that they exceed the threshold\nneeded for posterior displacement. Interestingly, this robustness originates in\ncell mechanics rather than biochemical networks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Feb 2017 11:06:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 10 Apr 2017 16:02:11 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 24 May 2017 13:50:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 5 Apr 2018 14:02:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-06"}
