 proposes graph-based algorithms working in the \"sample space\" of the\nbiomolecular profiles of the patients to predict their phenotype or outcome,\nthus contributing to a novel research line in the framework of the Network\nMedicine.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 4 Feb 2017 11:18:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-07"}
